Ecology : This species is probably confined to estuaries of brackish mangrove rivers and is able to tolerate low salinities (
Carvacho, 1979
;
Christoffersen, 1982
). In Mar de Cananéia and Baía do Trapandé (São Paulo), it was collected at depths of 0.3–1.2 m . The ovigerous specimen from Paraná was dredged from the mud bottom at 22 m (
Christoffersen, 1982
).
